Interestingly, we found several formal similarities and conceptual links among the type 2 criteria for maximizing type 2 accuracy, maximizing type 2 reward, and calibrating confidence to a threshold level of accuracy. All of these have a close connection to the type 1 criterion that maximizes type 1 accuracy (\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
