				\begin{document}$${c}_{1}^{\mathrm{A}^*}$$\end{document}c1∗), being located either as close as possible to \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
